Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{I have no luck with 'em!}Tao không có may mắn với phụ nữ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'd rather be with an armadillo!}Tao thích con tatu hơn!
