Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, a customer?}Khách hàng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{Not even. Can't you tell he's straight?}Không phải.\NKhông thấy cậu ấy thẳng tưng à?
